remarks.para:
If the configuration specified in the parameter is null then the default configuration will be used, however if specified the value should adhere to the following JSON format:
{ "genesis_txn": "path/to/genesis/transaction/file" }
If the value of the genesis_txn key in the JSON is null then a default file will be used. If the file specified does not exist it will be created.

